{"tid":243944,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯搶4失敗 摩佬訪問未完不悅鬆人","createTime":"2017-05-15T04:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T05:55:15.000Z","uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"753dfe5ec3af8f48ce9346539694bf968bd535b1","tid":243944,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=dfefb7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯兵敗白鹿徑，正式宣佈爭奪前4好夢落空，當他賽後接受訪問時顯得不悅，未完成訪問就離開。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯周日在白鹿徑最後一戰以1:2不敵熱刺，賽後36戰得65分，比排第4的曼城少7分，肯定不能衝上前4，摩連奴賽後自是不悅，他接受天空體育訪問時顯得有點不耐煩。<br />\n<br />\n他在短短兩分鐘的訪問中，只回答了3個問題，大致又是提及人腳不整，出戰這場比賽非他所願。當被問到曼聯需要甚麼才可在來季爭奪英超冠軍時，他回應：「此刻我不想思考這事情，我只想那場必須出戰的決賽。」當記者想再提問第4條問題時，他不再回答就轉身離開。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯必須在5月24日歐霸盃決賽打敗阿積士，才可取得來季歐聯資格。"},{"pid":"aa9139248643cea93133432a7c20f7c85f67a1ec","tid":243944,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"爭四呢樣野真係冇人夠爺爺嚟"},{"pid":"e5fdd74c7c96a9e867e9058dbb010762aee2c27b","tid":243944,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爭四呢樣野真係冇人夠爺爺嚟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今年未爭到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279e981d5fd4ff1ad38ef1edc6a3731e46a6d28c","tid":243944,"uid":51529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qcevanwx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqcevanwx&h=7717f19d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"288b7ea4787045c81814472662a1005050724322","tid":243944,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:53:45.000Z","msg":"交下戲姐呢場有期望佢贏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f61d582f1c2e86442fa6b0d393ae829fbfc0372","tid":243944,"uid":4155,"like"